===================================================================================

                          Blade Runner  - The Final Cut 
            
                                   1080p AAC

             The Final Cut: Ridley Scott's definitive version of the film, 
             with numerous aesthetic alterations, new shots and remixed sound.

             The Final Cut is the only version over which Ridley Scott had 
             complete artistic control, as the Director's Cut production did 
             not place Scott directly in charge. 
             Released in 2007 as "25th Anniversary Edition""

             Note: This film should be on everyone's "must see"-list
